<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>CLING TO THE BIBLE</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Bible tuchak zingin thil dang cheng sangin,
 A thupiek lul leh thiengtho ching zingin;
 Thagau ipmute a thu pha'n a hihhalh,
 Thihna apat hinna thutiem a nei.

[V2]
 Bible tu zingin (2)
 Bible I Thaumei leh Puipa ahi.

[V3]
 2. Bible tuchak zingin suongmantam leh go,
 Puksiete hukdamna, hinna ahi;
 A lulzie mihiem hetsen guol loh ahi,
 Hawlin Aw Thagau a vangsakna chuh.

[V4]
 3. I keng-a di'n lampi-a thaumei ahi,
 Hatlaite puk lohna'n puipa ahi;
 Mi gilote dingin kinepna ahi,
 Teksie di'n mawlh leh Lehkhabu pha pen.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>428</hymn_number>
</song>